{"tid":1252363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔學「毛澤東」和「孫中山」攪革命，其實無咩用","createTime":"2019-06-23T03:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T23:45:13.000Z","uid":134071,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"abe98fd9ef53f2b508d3b97a8ecbb3e668e57137","tid":1252363,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T03:34:44.000Z","msg":"孫中山唔係靠人民革命推翻滿清， 係靠說服清朝官員袁世凱發動政變而推翻滿清。而且到最後， 袁世凱成功奪取所有大權， 孫中山都鬥唔過佢。（日本政府曾協助孫中山逃亡。）<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東後來推翻國民黨政權， 係因為兩大原因：<br />\n1） 蘇聯向中共提供大量軍事援助與裝備<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2017/07/26/830123.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F830123.html&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaGINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=6d674011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2017/07/26/830123.html</a><br />\n2） 美國很早便決定放棄支持國民黨<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.udn.com/amlink/26024716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.udn.com%2Famlink%2F26024716&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaGINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=8ee5585b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://blog.udn.com/amlink/26024716</a><br />\n<br />\n「毛澤東」和「孫中山」既故事， 教唔到大家攪革命， 但引證左一個道理：<strong>香港抗爭者如果沒有國際支持， 一定衰硬。</strong>"},{"pid":"6bdb32f86f329d440f96bb80662d5884cab0e064","tid":1252363,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T03:37:11.000Z","msg":"孫中山革命史<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/孫中山\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E5%AD%AB%E4%B8%AD%E5%B1%B1&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaGINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=7a3340f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/孫中山</a>"},{"pid":"a4ef925a45b3e38fae89d7f1b4929ee4505ed4e6","tid":1252363,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T03:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd